  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722570/extras/bf38db390f76cb68957f0bd21078897f.avif?t=1761593060\" width=605 height=170 /></span><br>It's Christmas time! Everyone is looking forward to it, including our girls! They have already put on their Christmas hats, so they are ready! Find all the gifts and don't get trapped.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722570/extras/d43bcf2389a54a47c4a26f2ca1fd0ab4.poster.avif?t=1761593060\" width=604 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722570/extras/d43bcf2389a54a47c4a26f2ca1fd0ab4.webm?t=1761593060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722570/extras/d43bcf2389a54a47c4a26f2ca1fd0ab4.mp4?t=1761593060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the game, your goal is to collect gifts and not get trapped. Solve the puzzles in the correct order and collect all the gifts!🎁<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722570/extras/30fe385fcaef96ae1db913a3133879ed.avif?t=1761593060\" width=605 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🎄   Well-drawn backgrounds and CGs<br></li><li>❄️   Live2D dynamic character<br></li><li>🥂   Christmas mood<br></li><li>⛄   CG Gallery Mode<br></li><li>🎅   Relaxing music<br></li><li>🎁   Puzzle game</li></ul>",
